'''2016年維爾茨堡火車襲擊事件'''是指[[2016年7月|2016年7月]]18日约21:00 [[CEST|CEST]]在[[德國|德國]]發生的一宗[[恐怖襲擊|恐怖襲擊]]事件，一名17岁[[阿富汗|阿富汗]]難民在來往[[特羅伊赫特林根|特羅伊赫特林根]]以及[[維爾茨堡|維爾茨堡]]的[[區域列車|區域列車]]上持刀及斧頭攻擊乘客，有4名[[香港|香港]]遊客受傷，當中2人重傷<ref name=yahoo01/>。此外，列车外还有1人受伤。<ref name="spiegel2"/><ref name="Suddeutsche1"/><ref name="NYTimes1">{{cite news | title=ISIS claims responsibility for ax attack on German train | publisher= New York Times | url=http://www.nytimes.com/2016/07/20/world/europe/germany-train-ax-attack.html | date=19 July 2016|accessdate=19 July 2016}}</ref>

列车上的4名伤者分别为一对夫妇、他们的女儿、女儿的男友，均为香港游客。<ref name="BBCfam">{{cite web|title=Germany axe attack: Assault on train in Wurzburg injured HK family|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-36827725|publisher=BBC|date=19 July 2016|accessdate=19 July 2016|archive-date=2016-07-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160721130632/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-36827725|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="thelocal19">{{cite web|title=Hand-painted Isis flag 'found in room of train attacker'|url=http://www.thelocal.de/20160718/several-injured-in-knife-attack-on-bavarian-regional-train|publisher=thelocal.de|date=19 July 2016|accessdate=19 July 2016|archive-date=2016-07-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160721081715/http://www.thelocal.de/20160718/several-injured-in-knife-attack-on-bavarian-regional-train|dead-url=no}}</ref>第5名伤者是当地的女性，在列车外遭到袭击。<ref name="spiegel2">{{cite web|title=Angriffe mit Vernichtungswillen|url=http://spiegel.de/panorama/justiz/a-1103754.html|publisher=[[Der_Spiegel|Der Spiegel]]|date=19 July 2016|accessdate=19 July 2016|archive-date=2019-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190912102910/https://www.spiegel.de/panorama/justiz/wuerzburg-angriffe-mit-vernichtungswillen-a-1103754.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Suddeutsche1">{{cite web|title=Was wir über den Angriff bei Würzburg wissen - und was nicht|url=http://www.sueddeutsche.de/bayern/anschlag-auf-zugreisende-was-wir-ueber-den-angriff-bei-wuerzburg-wissen-und-was-nicht-1.3084902|publisher=[[Süddeutsche_Zeitung|Süddeutsche Zeitung]]|date=19 July 2016|accessdate=19 July 2016|archive-date=2016-07-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160721193752/http://www.sueddeutsche.de/bayern/anschlag-auf-zugreisende-was-wir-ueber-den-angriff-bei-wuerzburg-wissen-und-was-nicht-1.3084902|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="NYTimes1"/>14人目击袭击后受驚過度，需接受治疗。<ref name="spiegel1">{{cite web|title=Mann attackiert Zugreisende mit Axt - vier Schwerverletzte|url=http://spiegel.de/panorama/justiz/a-1103596.html|publisher=[[Der_Spiegel|Der Spiegel]]|date=19 July 2016|accessdate=19 July 2016|archive-date=2019-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190912102910/https://www.spiegel.de/panorama/justiz/bei-wuerzburg-mann-attackiert-reisende-im-zug-mehrere-schwerverletzte-a-1103596.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="bbc1">{{cite web|title=Germany axe attack: Assault on train in Wurzburg|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-36827725|website=bbc.com|publisher=BBC|date=19 July 2016|accessdate=19 July 2016|archive-date=2016-07-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160721130632/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-36827725|dead-url=no}}</ref>

